INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2245,2,'2013-04-13 20:57:43','2013-04-14 00:57:43','[caption id=\"attachment_106\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"150\"]<a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/shop/the-essential-handbag/pagelines-purses81220120801_0122-jpg/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-106\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-106\" alt=\"The Essentials Handbag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/purses81220120801_0122-150x150.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> The Essentials Handbag[/caption]\n<h2>Wear Your Art!</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">These bags are not found in department stores. Instead, each purse is handmade by an artisan with every attention to detail. You will find that the resulting quality of these bags is exceptional.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">The size of the bag is perfect for a quick shopping trip. For a longer day, it\'s small and flexible and will easily fit in your briefcase or tote and keep all your essentials in one place.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">The wrist straps leave your hands free to carry a parcel or a baby. Or to scan the racks for those elusive perfect jeans.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">There is no shoulder strap to slide off your arm. The bags weigh only a few ounces and are light and easy to carry, helping you avoid neck and shoulder issues due to \"handbag syndrome\"\n</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">Brides love that these bags can hold all the bridal essentials, but leave their hands free for hugs, dances and drinking champagne.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">These bags are distinctive and stylish accessories that elicit constant comment.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">The workmanship 